  "text": "In order to evaluate the usefulness of imbalanced learning methods for sentiment classification, we performed computational experiments with four classifiers combined with twelve imbalanced learning methods. The experiments were performed in Python using the scikit-learn [CITATION_1] and imbalanced-learn [CITATION_2] libraries.",
